**Task Pull: POST /workers/tasks/pull (routes/tasks.rs)**
- Reclaims jobs from stale workers
- Fails jobs exceeding max_job_reclaims
- Fails jobs with expired leases
- Selects oldest pending job and assigns to worker
- Returns 204 No Content if no tasks available

**Task Complete: POST /workers/tasks/:id/complete (routes/tasks.rs)**
- Validates worker matches assignment
- Job must be in assigned/running state
- Success: assigned/running → completed
- Failure: assigned/running → failed
- Post-completion: publishes events, calls engine for workflow-specific follow-up

**Log Ingestion: POST /workers/tasks/:id/logs (routes/logs.rs)**
- Accepts SendLogsRequest with entries
- Looks up job to get session_id and worker_id
- Bulk inserts to database
- Broadcasts to SSE subscribers
- Dual-writes to local log file if log_dir configured
- Returns 202 Accepted

